trans-unit.source: Identifies the accessible element that is to be annotated.
trans-unit.target: 标识要批注的可访问元素。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the length of the string identified by the `pIDString` parameter.
trans-unit.target: 指定由标识字符串的长度`pIDString`参数。

trans-unit.source: Specifies an array of properties to be handled by the specified callback object.
trans-unit.target: 指定要由指定的回调对象的属性数组。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the number of properties in the `paProps` array.
trans-unit.target: 指定的数中的属性`paProps`数组。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the callback object that will be invoked when a client requests one of the overridden properties.
trans-unit.target: 指定在客户端请求的重写属性之一时将调用的回调对象。

trans-unit.source: May be ANNO_THIS, indicating that the annotation affects the indicated accessible element only; or ANNO_CONTAINER, indicating that it applies to the element and its immediate element children.
trans-unit.target: 可能是 ANNO_THIS，，该值指示批注影响指示可访问元素仅;或 ANNO_CONTAINER，指示它应用于元素和其即时元素子级。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="Accessibility.CAccPropServicesClass"></xref> and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) <xref uid="langword_csharp_IAccPropServices" name="IAccPropServices" href=""></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="Accessibility.CAccPropServicesClass"> </xref>及其所有公开的成员是否托管包装的组件对象模型 (COM) 的一部分<xref uid="langword_csharp_IAccPropServices" name="IAccPropServices" href=""></xref>接口。
